title: [Aniwaya's General Store]
[Aniwaya's Outfitting]
description: A framed Ta'Illistim map hangs on one of the painted emerald green walls, and a paneled haon ceiling rises overhead.  A verdant elderberry bush sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is a painted red cedar rack on one side of the shop and a painted red cedar rack on the other.
